Vulnerabilities.Title: Prototype Pollution in sheetJS
Vulnerabilities.Description: SheetJS Community Edition before 0.19.3 allows Prototype Pollution via a crafted file. In other words. 0.19.2 and earlier are affected, whereas 0.19.3 and later are unaffected.

Vulnerabilities.Title: SheetJS Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS)
Vulnerabilities.Description: SheetJS Community Edition before 0.20.2 is vulnerable.to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS).
